## §3 Frontend class/module names (TypeScript)

| Suffix / shape | Role | Examples |
|---|---|---|
| `*Page` | Top-level route component | `LoginPage`, `HomePage`, `PatientListPage` |
| `*Provider` | React context provider | `AuthProvider`, `QueryProvider` |
| `*Route` | Router-level wrapper | `ProtectedRoute`, `AppRouter` |
| `*.ts` (no suffix, kebab/single) | Library module under `src/lib/` | `api-client.ts`, `auth.ts`, `patients.ts`, `utils.ts` |
| `components/ui/*.tsx` (lowercase) | shadcn/ui primitive | `button.tsx`, `card.tsx`, `input.tsx`, `label.tsx` |
| `*.test.{ts,tsx}` | Colocated test | `auth.test.ts`, `PatientListPage.test.tsx` |

